     H            Y.
     F** AJVRR3 **********************************
     F*    CHECK RESULT TRANSFER DAT             *
     F*         CODING:A.MAMIYA     2003.06.15   *
     F********************************** AJVRR3 **
     FINPUT   IP  F     256            DISK
     IINPUT   AA  01
      *HD
     I                                        1   1 IHKBN
     I                                       46  50 IHREC
      *DT
     I                                        1   1 IDKBN
      *TO
     I                                        1   1 ITKBN
     I                                        2   6 ITREC
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        1   20TKOTI
     I                                        3   40TKOMI
     I                                        5   60TKOSE
     I                                        7  100TKOYY
     I                                       11  120TKOMM
     I                                       13  140TKODD
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PREC   100
     C                     PARM           PERR    1
     C                     PARM           PCNT    5
      *
     C                     ADD  1         WNO     50
      *----------*
      * CHECK HD *
      *----------*
     C           IHKBN     IFEQ 'H'
     C                     MOVE IHREC     WHREC   50
     C           PREC      IFNE WHREC
     C                     MOVEL'E'       PERR
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *----------*
      * CHECK DT
      *----------*
     C           IDKBN     IFEQ 'D'
     C                     ADD  1         WCNT    50
     C                     ENDIF
      *----------*
      * CHECK TO
      *----------*
     C           ITKBN     IFEQ 'T'
     C                     MOVE ITREC     WTREC   50
     C           WNO       IFNE WTREC
     C                     MOVEL'E'       PERR
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     CLR                   MOVE WCNT      PCNT
